flowchart LR
    Witness[raw witness] --> AppServer[codex app-server]
    AppServer -->|turn/start| LiveTurn[live commandExecution]
    LiveTurn -->|item/commandExecution/terminalInteraction| ProcessId[live processId]
    ProcessId -->|command/exec/write| WriteAttempt[same-connection write attempt]
    WriteAttempt --> Verdict{upstream verdict}
    Verdict -->|confirmed| Future[bounded transcript control bridge later]
    Verdict -->|rejected| Boundary[read-only terminal pane remains honest]
    Verdict -->|ambiguous| Stop[no product bridge claim]
